        <item>
            <title>Version 0.9.3</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 06:14:21 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[A big refresh of the menu bar and Advanced Settings. Per-display controls (brightness, color, resolution, layout) now live in one card. The Sleep Timer is redesigned with custom durations, a progress bar, and an Extend menu. Automation is grouped into collapsible sections, with a new Power and Comfort settings area. Larger tap targets in the menu bar, masked license and server keys, and clearer Presets with summaries.]]></description>
